          <h2 style="font-size:24px;line-height:1.2;font-weight:500; margin-top:2px !important">Ukraine retreats from Kursk</h2>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-image border-radius="10px" padding="10px 12px" width="600px" src="https://www.geopoliticalsummary.com/email/images/sudzha-town-kursk-region-ukrainian-army-entry.png" alt="View of the town of Sudzha in Russia's Kursk region after the Ukrainian army entered the area" href="https://www.geopoliticalsummary.com" />
